title: Goran Bregovic - Ederlezi (1998)@flac
description: An interesting compilation of his film music. There are tracks from all of his albums straight to famous "Underground". "Ederlezi" takes you on a journey through balkans ("Mesicina"), dark 15 century cities ("Ederlezi"), the meditareann culture ("Elo hi") and straight modern places ("Tv screen"). Still the best tracks from here are these from "Arizona dream" - one his most complex and exciting works. it is a great compilation of this artist - it ends just in hte time that he started to colaborate with many pop artists (Kayah,Kris krawczyk) which wansn't magical at all.
